Brazil Agriculture Minister to Have Surgery for Brain Tumor

-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r i s t o w
-- 
2011-10-15T13:26:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-15/brazil-agriculture-minister-to-have-surgery-for-brain-tumor.html
Mendes Ribeiro,  Brazil ’s minister of
agriculture, will undergo surgery today to remove a brain tumor,
according to an e-mailed statement from the Sirio-Libanes
hospital in  Sao Paulo .  During tests last week, doctors detected a “probable
recurrence” of a tumor that was removed in 2007, the statement
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Matthew Bristow in Brasilia at 
 mbristow5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Joshua Goodman  at 
 jgoodman19@bloomberg.net . 